* Status flags
* 
* #TABLE(default, default)
* { =h Bit | =h Purpose }
* { $00 | Set during warp }
* { $01 | Set when all waves are completed }
* { $02 | Set when you die }
* { $03 | Set during chance stage }
* { $04 | Set during stage init }
* { $05 | Set for two-player game when one is game over }
* { $06 | Set during main loop }
* { $07 | Two-player game }
* TABLE#
status_flags:                          ; >71eb
       byte >00

* Stars move countdown
