* 
* Set to 5 when starting a tune, but any non-zero value could be used. Set to 0
* when stopping a tune
is_tune_playing:                       ; >727a
       byte >00

* Sound player countdown (tune speed?)
* 
* Counts down from 5 to zero, and certain sound player actions are only
* performed when 0.
